        "custom_liquid": "<section style=\"background:#0d0d0d;color:#fff;padding:64px 32px;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;\"><h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(22px,4vw,30px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:10px;\">[REPLACE: Headline — e.g. 'Everything they hid from you — all in one book']</h2><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:40px;\">[REPLACE: Subheading — e.g. 'Ancient decoded knowledge. One book. Everything they never wanted you to find.']</p><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:0;text-align:left;\"><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 1 — e.g. 'The Bible is a map of your brain']</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 2 — e.g. 'Your pineal gland is deliberately calcified']</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 3]</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 4]</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 5]</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 6]</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 7]</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #222;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 8]</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 9]</div><div style=\"padding:13px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e0e0e0;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;min-width:6px;background:#f5a623;border-radius:50%;\"></span>[REPLACE: Secret point 10]</div></div></div></section>",
